org.apache.cassandra.io.sstable
Class SSTableMetadata

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.cassandra.io.sstable.SSTableMetadata

public class SSTableMetadata
extends java.lang.Object

Metadata for a SSTable. Metadata includes: - estimated row size histogram - estimated column count histogram - replay position - max column timestamp - compression ratio - partitioner - generations of sstables from which this sstable was compacted, if any An SSTableMetadata should be instantiated via the Collector, openFromDescriptor() or createDefaultInstance()
